h1 id=3D"develop-an-audio-enabled-chat-app">Develop an audio-enabled chat a=
pp</h1>
<p>In this exercise, you use the <em>Phi-4-multimodal-instruct</em> generat=
ive AI model to generate responses to prompts that include audio files. You=
'll develop an app that provides AI assistance for a produce supplier compa=
ny by using Azure AI Foundry and the Python OpenAI SDK to summarize voice m=
essages left by customers.</p>
<p>While this exercise is based on Python, you can develop similar applicat=
ions using multiple language-specific SDKs; including:</p>
<ul>
<li><a class=3D"icon-link external-link" href=3D"https://pypi.org/project/a=
zure-ai-projects" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window)">Azu=
re AI Projects for Python</a></li>
<li><a class=3D"icon-link external-link" href=3D"https://pypi.org/project/o=
penai/" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window)">OpenAI librar=
y for Python</a></li>
<li><a class=3D"icon-link external-link" href=3D"https://www.nuget.org/pack=
ages/Azure.AI.Projects" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window=
)">Azure AI Projects for Microsoft .NET</a></li>
<li><a class=3D"icon-link external-link" href=3D"https://www.nuget.org/pack=
ages/Azure.AI.OpenAI" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window)"=
>Azure OpenAI client library for Microsoft .NET</a></li>
<li><a class=3D"icon-link external-link" href=3D"https://www.npmjs.com/pack=
age/@azure/ai-projects" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window=
)">Azure AI Projects for JavaScript</a></li>
<li><a class=3D"icon-link external-link" href=3D"https://www.npmjs.com/pack=
age/@azure/openai" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window)">Az=
ure OpenAI library for TypeScript</a></li>
